OL,6,F"The period of antenatal care, whether
OL,7,Fthat is by a midwife, an obstetrician,
OL,8,Fsometimes an anaesthetist might be
OL,9,Finvolved, ultrasound scanning, is a
OL,10,Freally crucial time," she said.
OL,12,FShe adds: "The quality of that care
OL,13,Fcan really impact on how well a mother
OL,14,Fand her baby, or her babies are, as
OL,15,Fthey go into labour.
OL,17,F"I can't stress enough the importance
OL,18,Fof ensuring that all women have the
OL,19,Fhighest standards of care."
