OL,6,FThe expansion of the review to include
OL,7,Fantenatal care comes at the same time,
OL,8,Fa national landmark inquiry into birth
OL,9,Ftrauma found 'good care was the
OL,10,Fexception rather than the rule."
OL,12,FMs Ockenden said: "Women and families
OL,13,Fand their babies in this country
OL,14,Fdeserve better.
OL,16,F"We have to honour the 1,500 families
OL,17,Fof Shrewsbury, the more than 1,900
OL,18,Ffamilies who are part of this review
OL,19,Fin Nottingham and the 1,300 families
OL,20,Fwho actually contributed to the birth
OL,21,Ftrauma inquiry."
